title: Do Your Data Recovery 5.0.0 (Install + Portable)
description:
*** About this release

Release date: 22/04/2016
Versions included: Professional, Technician, Enterprise, Advanced PE
See Edition comparision http://www.doyourdata.com/data-recovery-software/
Install: run installer, do not run software, copy your preferred patched version to installation directory
Portable: Technician Edition, already patched, unpack and run Main executable

Improvements & New Features

- Optimize algorithms and boost the speed of deep scan.
- Improve raw recovery quality.
- Better support for NTFS file system and HFS file system.

*** About Do Your Data Recovery

All-in-one, feature-rich data recovery service software to recover all types of lost files.
It is the best choice for service provider, company and business usage.

Do Your Data Recovery Technician edition is the best data recovery service software that allows to recover lost data from PC, laptop, hard drive, digital device, storage media, Server, RAID etc. The unlimited usage data recovery software allows you to recover lost files from different PCs or devices, so it's best choice for service providers, technicians, company or business.

- Powerful Data Recovery Capacity
Recover lost data due to deleting, formatting, partition loss, OS crash, file system crash etc.
Secure data recovery from PC, laptop, hard drive, RAID, Server, digital device or other storage media.
Support to recover all types of files, such as photos, emails, videos, documents, folders, audio etc.
Two recovery modes - Quick Recovery, Advanced Recovery to ensure finding all missing files.

- Preview before Recovery
Normally, the quick recovery finds deleted or recently lost files quickly and the advanced recovery will take more time to scan your device and find much more lost files. Thousands of lost files maybe found, you're able to filter or preview these files before you decide to recover them.

- Easy-to-use and Cost-effective Data Recovery Software
Only 3 simple steps to get all lost data back.
100% safe, no overwrite, no damage.

Homepage http://www.doyourdata.com/
